(3231, 1568, 'extra', 'Na de eruptie van de Mount Mazama  7700 jaar geleden bleef een van de diepste meren van de wereld over :  592 meter diep.\r\nThe deep blue lake is the deepest lake in the U.S.A.  1943 feet .\r\nWizard Island in the middle erupted after the lake began to fill ; \r\nonly with rain and snow .\r\nMount Mazama , one of a line of volcanoes  along the Pacific Ocean ,from California into British Colombia .\r\nBritish Colombia'),
