 peace and saving people and the planet[/caption]', 'Peter Lucker', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-03-17 19:06:05', '2022-03-17 19:06:05', '', 5, 'http://www.peterlucker-arts.com/?p=1508', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
